CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

May 10, 2013

[Cite as 05110/2013 Case Announcements, 2013-0hio-1910.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2013-0336. State ex rel. Redding v. Gallagher.

In Procedendo. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of procedendo.

Upon consideration of relator’s motion to supplement writ of procedendo with accompanying affidavits pursuant to R.C. 2969.25(A) and 2969.25(C), it is ordered by the court that the motion is denied as moot.
